# Driftara Gallery (`image-scoring-gallery`)

## Project Overview

This is a high-performance image gallery application built with Electron, React, and Vite. It serves as a frontend for browsing and filtering images scored by **Vexlum Scoring** (`image-scoring-backend`).

## Core Technologies

- **Frontend**: React 19, TypeScript 5.9
- **Build Tool**: Vite 7
- **Electron**: 40.1.0
- **Database**: Firebird SQL (via `node-firebird`)
- **Styling**: Vanilla CSS + CSS Modules (tokens in `src/styles/tokens.css`, layout in `src/styles/layout.css`, base resets in `src/index.css`); design system in [`docs/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`](docs/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md)
- **State Management**: Zustand 5
- **UI Components**: Lucide React, React Virtuoso

## Key Entry Points

- `electron/main.ts` - Main process entry
- `src/main.tsx` - Renderer process entry
- `electron/db.ts` - Firebird database integration
- `run.bat` - Application launcher

